@{
  ViewBag.Title = "Game";
}
@section HeadContent{
  @Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jquery")
  @Scripts.Render("~/bundles/gamescripts")
}
<html>
<head>
  <title></title>
 
</head>

<body>
  <audio id="music" src="~/GameCode/assets/art/TheTimes.mp3" loop="loop" preload="auto" autoplay="autoplay"></audio>
  <div class="controlsShowHide"><a onclick="ToggleControls(this)">CLICK ME!</a></div>
  <section class="plaque controls">
      <aside class="plaque_section">
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer rhoncus ligula vitae orci pellentesque, eleifend sollicitudin quam tempus. Praesent rhoncus nunc nec dolor molestie, a tempor ante lobortis. Maecenas laoreet, libero nec posuere venenatis, ex massa mattis mi, ac cursus lorem felis lobortis felis. Curabitur vel lectus sed tortor rhoncus condimentum sagittis a nunc. Integer id eros pretium, imperdiet augue vel, condimentum ligula. Etiam id sollicitudin tellus. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>
      </aside>     
  </section>
  <div id="screenPosition" style="margin-top:180px; position:absolute;"></div>
  <div class="game_canvas">
    <div id="canvas_container">
      <div class="playPause_button">
        <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="document.getElementById('music').muted = !document.getElementById('music').muted; return false"><img src="~/Content/Images/sound.png" id="mute_btn" /></a>
      </div>
      <a href="#screenPosition"><img src="~/Content/Images/reposition.png" id="reposition" /></a>
      <canvas id="display_canvas" style="border:2px solid #d4af37;"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-2.1.3.js"></script>
    <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        function start() {
            sidescroller_game.run();
        }
        window.onload = start;
    </script>
    <script>
        (function () {
            var ControlsSection = document.getElementsByClassName('controls')[0];

            var isShownRegex = /(^|\s)Shown(\s|$)/;

            window.ToggleControls = function (elem) {
                if (!ControlsSection) return;

                if (isShownRegex.test(ControlsSection.className)) {
                    ControlsSection.className = ControlsSection.className.replace(isShownRegex, ' ');
                } else {
                    ControlsSection.className += ' Shown';
                }
                ControlsSection.className = ControlsSection.className.trim();
            }
        })()

    </script>
</body>
</html>